Package: awdb
Title: Query the USDA NWCC Air and Water Database REST API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kenneth", "Vernon", , "kenneth.b.vernon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0098-5092"))
Description: The awdb package provides functions for querying the four endpoints
    of the USDA NWCC Air and Water Database REST API, including data, forecast, 
    reference-data, and metadata. The package is extremely light weight, with 
    Rust via extendr doing most of the heavy lifting to deserialize and flatten 
    deeply nested JSON responses.
